  "texts": [
    "A higher temperature value leads to more randomness in the output.",
    "In other words, it raises the likelihood of selecting tokens other than the most probable ones.",
    "However, with a temperature setting of 0, chatbots generate responses by selecting the next words with the highest probability.",
    "Therefore, this selection leads to more deterministic behavior of chatbots.",
    "Prompt engineering enables the design and optimization of input prompts to instruct LLMs in performing specific tasks."
  ],
